3. Third-party material
-----------------------

This reference cites and quotes primary definitional authorities, including the
SaaS Metrics Standards Board and the origin authors of coined metrics. Those
verbatim quotations, and any captured source snapshots under
`definitions/evidence/`, remain the property of their respective authors and are
reproduced here for reference and attribution. The CC BY 4.0 license in section 1
covers Sculpted Systems' own contribution (the codification, structure,
reconciliation, and classification), not the underlying quoted material, which is
governed by its own terms.
